api.github.com/repos/mvanhorn/cli-printing-press/labels/priority:P3","name":"priority:P3","color":"adca0b","default":false,"description":""},{"id":10856113676,"node_id":"LA_kwDORunh1s8AAAAChxMmDA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvanhorn/cli-printing-press/labels/comp:generator","name":"comp:generator","color":"a2bad1","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2026-05-19T18:42:47Z","updated_at":"2026-05-24T03:30:32Z","closed_at":"2026-05-24T03:30:32Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"COLLABORATOR","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Problem\n\nGreptile flagged the generator-emitted `ftsRowID` helper in `internal/store/store.go` on mvanhorn/printing-press-library#701. `store.go` has a generated `DO NOT EDIT` header, so the fix belongs in the Printing Press store template rather than as a Kit-only hand edit.\n\nAffected printed path:\n\n- `library/marketing/kit/internal/store/store.go:763-773`\n- Review thread: https://github.com/mvanhorn/printing-press-library/pull/701#discussion_r3268274097\n\nGreptile finding:\n\n> `ftsRowID` uses a simple polynomial roll (`h*31 + c`) over 64-bit integers with natural overflow. Two different `(scope, id)` pairs can produce the same rowid with non-negligible probability at scale. When a collision happens, `DELETE FROM resources_fts WHERE rowid = ?` silently removes the *wrong* FTS entry, leaving the deleted item searchable and making the new item invisible to search. Using `fnv.New64a` or the low 8 bytes of `crypto/sha256` would give a much flatter distribution at negligible extra cost.\n\n## Expected change\n\nUpdate the store template, likely `internal/generator/templates/store.go.tmpl`, to derive FTS5 rowids with `fnv.New64a` or `sha256[:8]` instead of the current polynomial hash. Include a focused test or golden fixture update so generated CLIs retain stable, lower-collision FTS rowid behavior.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvanhorn/cli-printing-press/issues/1671/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvanhorn/cli-printing-press/issues/1671/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/kit/issues/15869","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/kit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/kit/issues/15869/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/kit/issues/15869/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/kit/issues/15869/events","html_url":"https://github.com/sveltejs/kit/issues/15869","id":4477702241,"node_id":"I_kwDOEiPr8c8AAAABCuRQYQ","number":15869,"title":"Dev server reloads every 11 seconds","user":{"login":"MaddyGuthridge","id":31365175,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMxMzY1MTc1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/31365175?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge","html_url":"https://github.com/MaddyGuthridge","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MaddyGuthridge/received_event