":"type:feature","color":"a2eeef","default":false,"description":"New capability"},{"id":10815274503,"node_id":"LA_kwDOSPSdXM8AAAAChKP-Bw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/binsarjr/sveltego/labels/priority:p1","name":"priority:p1","color":"d93f0b","default":false,"description":"Important"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/binsarjr/sveltego/milestones/2","html_url":"https://github.com/binsarjr/sveltego/milestone/2","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/binsarjr/sveltego/milestones/2/labels","id":15720965,"node_id":"MI_kwDOSPSdXM4A7-IF","number":2,"title":"v0.2 — Form Actions & Hooks","description":"Form actions, hooks chain, error boundary, +server.go.","creator":{"login":"binsarjr","id":33781288,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzgxMjg4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/33781288?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr","html_url":"https://github.com/binsarjr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/binsarjr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":15,"state":"open","created_at":"2026-04-28T21:18:54Z","updated_at":"2026-04-30T08:59:15Z","due_on":"2026-08-31T00:00:00Z","closed_at":null},"comments":0,"created_at":"2026-04-28T22:23:30Z","updated_at":"2026-04-30T06:32:16Z","closed_at":"2026-04-30T06:32:16Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Summary\n\nSupport page-level options exported as constants from `+page.server.go` / `+layout.server.go`: `Prerender`, `SSR`, `CSR`, `TrailingSlash`. Already partially in #65 (Prerender); this issue wires the remaining three plus a unified plumbing.\n\n## Background\n\nSvelteKit lets routes opt out of SSR (`ssr = false` for client-only rendered pages), opt out of CSR (`csr = false` for static-feeling pages with no JS), and customize trailing-slash policy. Same constants apply at layout level and cascade.\n\n## Goals\n\n- [ ] Recognize exported constants `Prerender`, `SSR`, `CSR`, `TrailingSlash` in `+page.server.go` and `+layout.server.go`.\n- [ ] `SSR=false`: skip server render; serve static shell + hydrate client.\n- [ ] `CSR=false`: skip client bundle injection; HTML only.\n- [ ] `TrailingSlash` values: `Never` (default), `Always`, `Ignore`.\n- [ ] Layout-level options cascade to descendants unless overridden.\n- [ ] Manifest carries effective values per route.\n\n## Non-Goals\n\n- Per-action options.\n- Dynamic toggling at request time.\n\n## Detailed Design\n\n```go\n// +page.server.go\npackage page\n\nimport \"github.com/binsarjr/sveltego/kit\"\n\nconst (\n    Prerender     = false\n    SSR           = false\n    CSR           = true\n    TrailingSlash = kit.TrailingSlashNever\n)\n\nfunc Load(ctx kit.LoadCtx) (PageData, error) { /* ... */ }\n```\n\nCodegen reads constants via `go/ast`. Manifest entry includes resolved options. Pipeline (#20) branches:\n\n- `SSR=false`: emit `<div id=\"app\"></div>` + payload + bundle; skip Render.\n- `CSR=false`: emit Render output but no script tags; payload optional.\n- `TrailingSlash=Always` redirects `/foo` → `/foo/`; `Never` does the inverse.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `SSR=false` route renders empty shell server-side; client hydrates from data.\n- [ ] `CSR=false` route returns HTML with no `<script type=\"module\">` for the bundle.\n- [ ] `TrailingSlash=Always` issues 308 redirect.\n- [ ] Layout-level option cascades; page-level overrides.\n- [ ] Build errors for unknown values.\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n- Integration: HTTP tests for each option combo.\n- Golden: manifest values for fixture project.\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Headers customization per page (use hooks instead).\n\n## Risks & Open Questions\n\n- `SSR=false` interacts with prerender: if both, pre-emit empty shell.\n- Cascade ordering precise — document and test.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Blocks: real-world page customization.\n- Blocked by: #15, #20, #65.\n\n## References\n\n- SvelteKit page options: https://kit.svelte.dev/docs/page-options\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/binsarjr/sveltego/issues/79/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/binsarjr/sveltego/issues/79/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303/events","html_url":"https://github.com/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303","id":4507905289,"node_id":"I_kwDOSfQcDc8AAAABDLEtCQ","number":303,"title":"Spec Kit CLI main ブランチ導入: .specify/ 追加・speckit-* スキル登録・ADR 0002 確定","user":{"login":"squne121","id":63350259,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYzMzUwMjU5","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/63350259?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121","html_url":"https://github.com/squne121","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/squne121/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":10995862709,"node_id":"LA_kwDOSfQcDc8AAAACj2eMtQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/labels/phase/implementation","name":"phase/implementation","color":"0075ca","default":false,"description":"Implementation phase"},{"id":11029446132,"node_id":"LA_kwDOSfQcDc8AAAACkWf99A","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/labels/kind/implementation","name":"kind/implementation","color":"0075ca","default":false,"description":"Implementation issue"},{"id":11029448990,"node_id":"LA_kwDOSfQcDc8AAAACkWgJHg","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/labels/area/ai-ops","name":"area/ai-ops","color":"0e8a16","default":false,"description":"AI operations and agent tooling area"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":7,"created_at":"2026-05-23T11:23:36Z","updated_at":"2026-05-23T12:56:43Z","closed_at":"2026-05-23T12:54:36Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Machine-Readable Contract\n\n```yaml\ncontract_schema_version: v1\nissue_kind: implementation\nparent_issue: \"#298\"\ngoal_ref: \"#298 spec_kit_spike_acceptance 条件付き PASS を受け、Spec Kit CLI を main ブランチに正式導入する\"\nchange_kind: feature\n```\n\n## Parent Goal Ref\n\n- Goal: ADR 0002（accepted-with-deferral）の throwaway spike 完了条件を満たし、Spec Kit CLI を main ブランチに正式導入する\n- Desired Destination（parent #298 scope）: spike ワークツリーで spec_kit_spike_acceptance 6 項目が PASS し、後続導入 Issue が起票されていること\n\n## Parent Issue\n\n#298（spike 完了済み）\n#254（SDD adoption parent）\n\n## Background\n\nIssue #298 の throwaway worktree spike が完了し、`spec_kit_spike_acceptance` 6 項目がすべて条件付き PASS 以上となった。\nADR 0002 の `accepted-with-deferral` 決定に基づく「throwaway worktree spike 後に別 Issue で確定する」条件を満たしたため、本 Issue で main ブランチへの正式導入を実施する。\n\n## Spike 結果サマリ（#298 より）\n\n- specify-cli v0.8.13 インストール済み\n- `specify init --here --no-git --integration claude --force` を throwaway worktree で実行\n- `docs/` SSOT への書き込みなし（条件付き PASS）\n- `.specify/` 生成物は `docs/ssot-registry.md` を上書きしない（PASS）\n- main worktree の `.claude/skills/` / `.claude/commands/` への書き込みなし（条件付き PASS）\n- `/speckit.implement` 静的確認のみ実施（干渉なし、条件付き PASS）\n- round-trip 検証実現可能性あり（条件付き PASS）\n\n## Outcome\n\nSpec Kit CLI が main ブランチに正式導入され、ADR 0002 が `accepted` に更新される。\n\n## In Scope\n\n1. `.specify/` ディレクトリを main ブランチに手動マージ（throwaway worktree の生成物を整理してコミット）\n2. `speckit-*` スキルを upstream 名（`speckit-*`）のまま `.claude/skills/` に追加（upstream-compatible 優先）\n3. `docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に各 speckit スキルの責務境界を記録（`speckit-implement` は direct use prohibited / impl-review-loop 経由必須として明記すること）\n4. ADR 0002 を `accepted-with-deferral` → `accepted` に更新\n5. `docs/dev/ssot-registry.md` に `.specify/` を derived artifact として登録\n\n## Current Validated Scope\n\n- `.specify/` ディレクトリを main ブランチにコミット\n- `.claude/skills/speckit-*/` を upstream 名のまま追加\n- `docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md` を `accepted` に更新\n- `docs/dev/ssot-registry.md` に `.specify/` を derived artifact として登録\n- `docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に speckit スキル責務境界を記録\n\n## Remaining Parent Gaps\n\n- C254-2〜C254-8 の product docs 整備（別 child Issue 群の責務）\n- `speckit-*` スキルの spec-* namespace へのリネーム（upstream-compatible 優先のため非実施）\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- throwaway worktree での追加 spike\n- `/speckit.implement` の実行（ADR 0002 `implementation_execution_policy.direct_speckit_implement_on_main: prohibited` より禁止）\n- C254-2〜C254-8 の product docs（別 child Issue の責務）\n- `speckit-*` スキルの `spec-*` namespace へのリネーム（upstream-compatible 優先のため）\n\n## Required Skills\n\n- specify-cli v0.8.13（`specify init` / `.specify/` 生成物の取り扱い）\n- bash / git（worktree マージ・コミット操作）\n- Markdown ADR フォーマット（`docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md` 更新）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC1: `.specify/` ディレクトリが main ブランチにコミットされていること\n- [ ] AC2: `docs/` への変更は ADR 0002、`docs/dev/ssot-registry.md` 等の許可ファイルに限定されており、Spec Kit 生成物による SSOT 上書きが発生していないこと\n- [ ] AC3: `speckit-*` スキル 9 本が exact set で `.claude/skills/` に upstream 名のまま追加され、`docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に責務境界が記録されていること\n- [ ] AC3b: `docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に `speckit-implement` が \"direct execution prohibited / impl-review-loop 経由必須\" として明記されていること\n- [ ] AC4: ADR 0002 が以下の条件をすべて満たして更新されていること\n  - `status: accepted` に更新されている\n  - `speckit-*` upstream 名採用が `spec-` prefix 方針の明示的な後続決定として記録されている\n  - `.claude/skills/speckit-*` は reviewed upstream snapshot / managed derived artifact として扱うと明記されている\n  - `direct_speckit_implement_on_main: prohibited` が維持されている\n  - `docs/` SSOT wins / `.specify/` derived workbench の境界が維持されている\n- [ ] AC5: `pnpm typecheck && pnpm lint && pnpm test && pnpm build` がすべて pass すること\n- [ ] AC6: 250 行超の `speckit-*` SKILL.md ファイルについて、`docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に Tier 3 / 常時読込禁止として記録されていること。また `CLAUDE.md` / `.claude/rules/` に speckit スキルの常時読込指示が含まれていないこと\n- [ ] AC7: `.specify/` に provenance ファイルが存在し、specify-cli バージョン・upstream tag・生成コマンド・生成日時が記録されていること\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# AC1: .specify/ ディレクトリが main にコミットされていること\n- test -d .specify && echo \"PASS: AC1 .specify exists\" || echo \"FAIL: AC1 .specify missing\"\n\n# AC2: docs/ への変更が許可ファイルに限定されていること（生成物による上書きなし）\n# ADR 0002 と ssot-registry.md の変更は許容。それ以外の docs/ 変更がないこと\n- git diff main --name-only -- docs/ | grep -v \"docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md\" | grep -v \"docs/dev/ssot-registry.md\" | grep -v \"docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md\" \\\n  && echo \"FAIL: AC2 unexpected docs/ changes found\" || echo \"PASS: AC2 docs/ changes limited to allowed files\"\n\n# AC3: speckit-* スキル 9 本が exact set で存在すること\n- expected=$(printf '%s\\n' \\\n  speckit-analyze \\\n  speckit-checklist \\\n  speckit-clarify \\\n  speckit-constitution \\\n  speckit-implement \\\n  speckit-plan \\\n  speckit-specify \\\n  speckit-tasks \\\n  speckit-taskstoissues | sort)\n\n- actual=$(find .claude/skills -mindepth 1 -maxdepth 1 -type d -name 'speckit-*' -exec basename {} \\; | sort)\n\n- diff -u <(printf '%s\\n' \"$expected\") <(printf '%s\\n' \"$actual\") \\\n  && echo \"PASS: AC3 exact 9 speckit skills present\" \\\n  || { echo \"FAIL: AC3 speckit skill set mismatch\"; exit 1; }\n\n- for s in $expected; do\n  test -f \".claude/skills/$s/SKILL.md\" \\\n    || { echo \"FAIL: missing .claude/skills/$s/SKILL.md\"; exit 1; }\n  done\n- echo \"PASS: AC3 all speckit SKILL.md files present\"\n# agent-skill-boundaries.md に記録されていること\n- rg \"speckit\" docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md && echo \"PASS: AC3 agent-skill-boundaries.md updated\" || echo \"FAIL: AC3 agent-skill-boundaries.md not updated\"\n\n# AC4: ADR 0002 が accepted に更新されていること\n- rg \"status.*accepted\" docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md | grep -v \"accepted-with-deferral\" && echo \"PASS: AC4 ADR 0002 accepted\" || echo \"FAIL: AC4 ADR 0002 not updated\"\n\n# AC5: 品質ゲート\n- pnpm typecheck && pnpm lint && pnpm test && pnpm build && echo \"PASS: AC5 quality gates\" || echo \"FAIL: AC5 quality gates\"\n\n# AC6: 250行超 speckit SKILL.md の Tier 3 記録確認\n- for f in .claude/skills/speckit-*/SKILL.md; do\n  lines=\"$(wc -l < \"$f\" | tr -d ' ')\"\n  skill=\"$(basename \"$(dirname \"$f\")\")\"\n  if [ \"$lines\" -gt 250 ]; then\n    rg -n \"$skill\" docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md | grep -q \"Tier 3\\|常時読込禁止\\|auto.load prohibited\" \\\n      && echo \"PASS: AC6 $skill ($lines lines) Tier 3 documented\" \\\n      || { echo \"FAIL: AC6 $skill is $lines lines but Tier 3 not documented\"; exit 1; }\n  fi\n  done\n# 常時読み込み導線がないこと\n- ! rg -n \"speckit-.*(always|常時|必ず読む|autoload|auto-load)\" CLAUDE.md .claude/rules docs/dev 2>/dev/null \\\n  && echo \"PASS: AC6 no always-load speckit policy\" \\\n  || { echo \"FAIL: AC6 speckit always-load policy found\"; exit 1; }\n\n# AC7: .specify/ provenance 確認\n- test -f \".specify/provenance/spec-kit-main-introduction.yml\" \\\n  && rg \"specify_cli_version|upstream_tag|generation_command|generated_at\" .specify/provenance/spec-kit-main-introduction.yml \\\n  && echo \"PASS: AC7 provenance file exists\" \\\n  || echo \"FAIL: AC7 provenance file missing or incomplete\"\n```\n\n## Allowed Paths\n\n- `.specify/` — 新規追加（Spec Kit CLI 生成物）\n- `.claude/skills/speckit-*/` — 新規追加（upstream 名のまま）\n- `docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md` — ADR 更新\n- `docs/dev/ssot-registry.md` — derived artifact 登録\n- `docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` — speckit スキル責務境界記録\n- 上記以外の `docs/` への書き込み禁止\n- `src/` への書き込み禁止\n\n## Stop Conditions\n\n- Spec Kit 生成物が `docs/` SSOT を上書きしようとした場合は即停止\n- main worktree で `specify init` を直接実行しようとした場合は即停止（throwaway 由来でない `.claude/skills/speckit-*` 変更を検出した場合も即停止）\n- `/speckit.implement` を実行しようとした場合は即停止\n- Allowed Paths 外のファイル（`.claude/commands/**`, `CLAUDE.md`, `.github/**`, `src/**` など）を変更しようとした場合は即停止\n- `pnpm build` が失敗した場合は修正してから次へ進む\n- 権限不足（permission denied）により操作が完了できない場合は即停止\n\n## Preconditions\n\n- spike 結果コメント: https://github.com/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/298#issuecomment-4525161098\n- ADR 0002: `docs/adr/0002-sdd-tool-adoption.md`\n- specify-cli v0.8.13 がインストール済み（`specify --version` で確認）\n- PR #302 との前後関係: #302（ssot-catalog.md 削除・ssot-registry.md 正本化）が先に merge された場合、本 Issue の `docs/dev/ssot-registry.md` 更新は #302 の変更ベースで実施すること。#302 が未 merge の場合は rebase 後に競合確認を必須とする\n\n## Required Guardrails（ADR 0002 より）\n\n- `.specify/memory/constitution.md` を `docs/` SSOT の上位に置かない\n- `speckit-*` スキルは `.claude/skills/` に配置し、`docs/dev/agent-skill-boundaries.md` に責務境界を登録する（upstream 名 `speckit-*` のまま維持）\n- `tasks.md` は staging artifact として扱い、GitHub Issues materialize 後は archived に降格\n- SKILL.md のうち 250 行超（checklist/specify/analyze/clarify）は Tier 3 扱いで常時読込禁止\n\n## Runtime Verification Applicability\n\n`deferred` — PR マージ後の CI 実行で確認。\n- destination_type: pr_ci\n- destination_ref: （本 Issue を Close する PR の CI ランURL、マージ後に記録）\n- deferred_verification_condition: >\n    `pnpm typecheck && pnpm lint && pnpm test && pnpm build` が CI 上で全件 PASS し、\n    AC1〜AC4 の bash VC コマンドが PASS 出力を返すこと\n\n## Source\n\n```\nsource: impl-review-loop (issue #298)\ndedupe_key: spec-kit-main-branch-introduction\nanchor: https://github.com/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/298#issuecomment-4525168824\n```\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/squne121/loop-protocol/issues/303/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0}],"search_type":"lexical"}